narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I loved the speaker visits and being able to meet so many great people at talks and dinners. Feedback during class sessions was very helpful, and Alicia and Steve were great discussion leaders. I wish we had more incentive to do the readings, which began to feel optional after a while.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Absolutely! A very flexible way to improve whatever kinds of skills you think need improvement. Great speakers and great classmates.
